  "description": "We usually drink this coffee on the weekends for breakfast, since we both have good memories when we drink it. It reminds Margarita of her childhood, of the first time she drank coffee in Mexico, of countless breakfasts with her family and friends, chitchatting for hours. It reminds Artem of his dad in Russia, and the smell of his kitchen when he prepares it in a cezve.\n\nAnd now it creates new memories of both of us: reading in the kitchen, making plans for the day (mostly cooking plans), talking about everything and nothing. ",
